Convert-Color-ScaleModels

This module converts between color numbers from scale model paint manufacturers (Humbrol, Revell, Tamiya).
The lookup table is based on Humbrol's own conversion tables (http://humbrol.com/convert-to-humbrol/conversion-tables/).

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Convert::Color::ScaleModels

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Convert-Color-ScaleModels

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Convert-Color-ScaleModels

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Convert-Color-ScaleModels

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Convert-Color-ScaleModels/


